name: #11 Gatotkaca
description:
The Hero of Pandava, The Son of Bima and the Champion of Pringgadani
As an infant, Gatotkaca was shaped by the Gods to defeat a raging giant king. The tale of Bharatayuddha was filled with his heroic endeavors. 
In the Great War, he met his match, as Karna wields the only weapon that can kill Gatotkaca.


-Gatotkaca The Steel-

Base token for :
- Gatotkaca Brajadenta
- Gatotkaca Brajamusti
- Gatotkaca Narantaka
- Gatotkaca Esmugunting

- This token is treated as 'Gatotkaca' token -
